---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Kaldon — The Team Behind the Pipeline"
  description="Kaldon was built by eCommerce sellers who were tired of stitching together 6 tools to launch a product. Meet the team and learn why we built it."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#22d3ee]/5 via-[#0a0e17] to-[#0a0e17]"></div>
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 text-center">
      <span class="eyebrow">ABOUT</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#e2e8f0] mb-4">Built by Sellers.<br/>For Sellers.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#94a3b8] max-w-2xl mx-auto">Kaldon was not built in a Silicon Valley office. It was built in the trenches of eCommerce, by people who have launched products, managed inventory, and stayed up at 2am optimizing PPC campaigns.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin Story -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <div class="bg-[#111827] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mb-6">The Origin Story</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">
          <p>In 2024, our founder Sean Travis was launching his fourth eCommerce brand. He had the process down: research products in Helium 10, design the brand in Canva, write content in Jasper, schedule posts in Later, build the store in Shopify, and manage ads in Meta.</p>
          <p>Six tools. Six logins. Six subscriptions totaling over $300 per month. And the worst part? None of them talked to each other. Every time he found a winning product, he spent 200+ hours manually transferring data between platforms, re-entering the same information, and trying to maintain brand consistency across disconnected tools.</p>
          <p>The product research was excellent. The tools were excellent. But the workflow was broken. The gap was not in any individual tool. The gap was between them.</p>
          <p>So he started building. What if product research data automatically became a brand brief? What if the brand identity automatically applied to every piece of content? What if the content automatically populated a store? What if the store data automatically optimized the ads?</p>
          <p>That question became Kaldon: a single platform where every phase of launching and growing an eCommerce product is connected. Not bolted together. Not integrated through Zapier. Connected at the data layer, so intelligence flows from research to revenue without manual intervention.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="section-spacing bg-[#111827]/30">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl text-center">
      <span class="eyebrow">OUR MISSION</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mb-6">Make launching an eCommerce product<br/>as simple as having the idea.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">The barrier to eCommerce should not be technical complexity. It should not be how many tools you can afford or how many hours you can spend learning software. The only barrier should be having a good product idea. Kaldon handles everything else.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] text-center mb-12">What We Believe</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-[#111827] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)] rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#22d3ee]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#22d3ee]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mb-2">Intelligence Over Data</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8]">Raw data is not useful if you do not know what to do with it. Every output from Kaldon is a recommendation, not a spreadsheet. We tell you what to do, not just what the numbers say.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#111827] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)] rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#fb923c]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#fb923c]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mb-2">Connection Over Collection</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8]">Features that do not connect are just features. We build every capability to feed the next one. Your research becomes your brand. Your brand becomes your content. Your content becomes your revenue.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#111827] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)] rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#a78bfa]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#a78bfa]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mb-2">Honesty Over Hype</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8]">We do not promise overnight success. We do not claim AI will replace your judgment. We build tools that make your judgment better and your execution faster. The work is still yours. We just make it smarter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#111827] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)] rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#34d399]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#34d399]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mb-2">Accessibility Over Exclusivity</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8]">Professional-grade eCommerce intelligence should not require a $10,000 agency retainer or a decade of experience. We built Kaldon so that a first-time seller gets the same quality output as a 10-year veteran.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder -->
  <section class="section-spacing bg-[#111827]/30">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <span class="eyebrow">FOUNDER</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0]">Meet Sean Travis</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#111827] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#22d3ee] to-[#3b82f6] flex items-center justify-center text-[#0a0e17] font-bold text-2xl shrink-0">ST</div>
          <div class="text-center md:text-left">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0]">Sean Travis</h3>
            <p class="text-[#22d3ee] text-sm">Founder & CEO</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">
          <p>Sean has been building eCommerce businesses since 2019. He has launched products on Amazon, Walmart, and DTC, managed six-figure ad budgets, and experienced every pain point that Kaldon now solves.</p>
          <p>Before Kaldon, Sean ran eCommerce operations for multiple brands, learning firsthand that the biggest bottleneck was not finding good products. It was everything that came after: building the brand, creating the content, launching the store, and scaling the marketing. The tools existed, but the workflow was broken.</p>
          <p>Kaldon is the platform Sean wished he had when he launched his first product. It is built with the conviction that eCommerce should be accessible to anyone with a good idea and the willingness to work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-spacing relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#22d3ee]/10 via-[#0a0e17] to-[#a78bfa]/10"></div>
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#e2e8f0] mb-4">Join the Pipeline</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#94a3b8] mb-8">2 free analyses. No credit card. See what connected intelligence looks like.</p>
      <a href="https://kaldon.io/signup" class="btn-primary btn-large btn-glow inline-flex items-center gap-2">Start Free <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" /></svg></a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
